{"id":4090,"date":"2025-04-08T15:21:27","date_gmt":"2025-04-08T18:21:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/blog.primeiravendaonlinebr.com\/?page_id=4090"},"modified":"2025-04-08T15:29:44","modified_gmt":"2025-04-08T18:29:44","slug":"criador-de-storytelling-imagens","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/blog.primeiravendaonlinebr.com\/criador-de-storytelling-imagens\/","title":{"rendered":"Criador de Storytelling (Imagens)"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"4090\" class=\"elementor elementor-4090\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0eb5246 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"0eb5246\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8070543 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"8070543\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"storytelling-generator\" style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; background:#fff; padding:30px; max-width:800px; margin:auto; border-radius:10px; box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">\n  <h2 style=\"text-align:center; color:#111;\">\ud83c\udfac Criador de Storytelling - PVO<\/h2>\n\n  <label><strong>Nome do Produto:<\/strong><\/label>\n  <input type=\"text\" id=\"nomeProduto\" placeholder=\"Ex: M\u00e9todo Primeira Venda Online\" style=\"width:100%; padding:10px; margin:10px 0; border:1px solid #ccc; border-radius:5px;\">\n\n  <label><strong>Promessa Principal:<\/strong><\/label>\n  <input type=\"text\" id=\"promessa\" placeholder=\"Ex: Fa\u00e7a sua primeira venda online do zero em 7 dias\" style=\"width:100%; padding:10px; margin:10px 0; border:1px solid #ccc; border-radius:5px;\">\n\n  <label><strong>Storytelling \/ Hist\u00f3ria (curta):<\/strong><\/label>\n  <textarea id=\"historia\" rows=\"5\" placeholder=\"Ex: Eu comecei do zero, sem seguidores, e em 7 dias j\u00e1 estava ganhando...\" style=\"width:100%; padding:10px; border:1px solid #ccc; border-radius:5px;\"><\/textarea>\n\n  <label><strong>Estilo:<\/strong><\/label>\n  <select id=\"estilo\" style=\"width:100%; padding:10px; margin:10px 0; border-radius:5px; border:1px solid #ccc;\">\n    <option value=\"emocional\">Emocional<\/option>\n    <option value=\"direto\">Direto<\/option>\n    <option value=\"educativo\">Educativo<\/option>\n  <\/select>\n\n  <label><strong>Cor de Fundo:<\/strong><\/label>\n  <input type=\"color\" id=\"fundoCor\" value=\"#000000\" style=\"width:100%; height:40px; border:none; margin:10px 0;\">\n\n  <label><strong>Logo (opcional):<\/strong><\/label>\n  <input type=\"file\" id=\"logoUpload\" accept=\"image\/*\" style=\"margin-bottom:20px;\">\n\n  <button onclick=\"gerarStorytelling()\" style=\"background:#3FF000; color:#000; font-weight:700; padding:12px 20px; border:none; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; width:100%; font-size:16px;\">\ud83d\ude80 Gerar Storytelling<\/button>\n\n  <div id=\"imagensContainer\" style=\"margin-top:30px;\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<script src=\"https:\/\/cdnjs.cloudflare.com\/ajax\/libs\/html2canvas\/1.4.1\/html2canvas.min.js\"><\/script>\n<script>\nfunction gerarStorytelling() {\n  const nome = document.getElementById('nomeProduto').value.trim();\n  const promessa = document.getElementById('promessa').value.trim();\n  const historia = document.getElementById('historia').value.trim();\n  const estilo = document.getElementById('estilo').value;\n  const corFundo = document.getElementById('fundoCor').value;\n  const logoInput = document.getElementById('logoUpload');\n  const container = document.getElementById('imagensContainer');\n\n  if (!nome || !promessa || !historia) {\n    alert('Preencha todos os campos principais!');\n    return;\n  }\n\n  const roteiro = gerarRoteiro(nome, promessa, historia, estilo);\n  container.innerHTML = ''; \/\/ limpa imagens anteriores\n\n  const logoFile = logoInput.files[0];\n  const reader = new FileReader();\n\n  reader.onload = () => {\n    const logoData = logoFile ? reader.result : null;\n\n    roteiro.forEach((texto, index) => {\n      const card = document.createElement('div');\n      card.className = 'story-card';\n      card.style.width = '1080px';\n      card.style.height = '1920px';\n      card.style.background = corFundo;\n      card.style.color = '#fff';\n      card.style.display = 'flex';\n      card.style.flexDirection = 'column';\n      card.style.justifyContent = 'center';\n      card.style.alignItems = 'center';\n      card.style.textAlign = 'center';\n      card.style.padding = '80px 60px';\n      card.style.fontSize = '48px';\n      card.style.fontWeight = '700';\n      card.style.borderRadius = '20px';\n      card.style.marginBottom = '40px';\n      card.style.position = 'relative';\n      card.style.overflow = 'hidden';\n\n      const textoElem = document.createElement('div');\n      textoElem.innerText = texto;\n      card.appendChild(textoElem);\n\n      if (logoData) {\n        const logo = document.createElement('img');\n        logo.src = logoData;\n        logo.style.position = 'absolute';\n        logo.style.bottom = '60px';\n        logo.style.right = '60px';\n        logo.style.maxWidth = '160px';\n        logo.style.maxHeight = '160px';\n        card.appendChild(logo);\n      }\n\n      container.appendChild(card);\n\n      \/\/ Converter em imagem\n      html2canvas(card).then(canvas => {\n        const link = document.createElement('a');\n        link.download = `story-${index + 1}.png`;\n        link.href = canvas.toDataURL();\n        link.textContent = `\u2b07\ufe0f Baixar imagem ${index + 1}`;\n        link.style.display = 'inline-block';\n        link.style.marginBottom = '20px';\n        link.style.background = '#3FF000';\n        link.style.color = '#000';\n        link.style.padding = '10px 16px';\n        link.style.borderRadius = '6px';\n        link.style.textDecoration = 'none';\n        container.appendChild(link);\n      });\n    });\n  };\n\n  if (logoFile) {\n    reader.readAsDataURL(logoFile);\n  } else {\n    reader.onload();\n  }\n}\n\nfunction gerarRoteiro(nome, promessa, historia, estilo) {\n  if (estilo === 'emocional') {\n    return [\n      `\u26a1\ufe0f Voc\u00ea j\u00e1 sonhou com isso?\\n\\n${promessa}`,\n      `\ud83d\udcc9 Eu tamb\u00e9m comecei sem resultados...`,\n      `\ud83d\udca1 Foi a\u00ed que conheci o ${nome}`,\n      `\ud83d\udd25 ${historia}`,\n      `\u2705 Com o ${nome}, eu consegui:\\n\\n${promessa}`,\n      `\ud83d\udc49 Agora \u00e9 sua vez de fazer acontecer!`\n    ];\n  } else if (estilo === 'direto') {\n    return [\n      `\ud83d\ude80 Conhe\u00e7a o ${nome}`,\n      `\ud83c\udfaf Ele faz voc\u00ea:\\n\\n${promessa}`,\n      `\ud83d\udcc8 R\u00e1pido. Pr\u00e1tico. Simples.`,\n      `\ud83d\udcac ${historia}`,\n      `\ud83d\udcb8 Ideal pra quem quer resultado`,\n      `\ud83d\udd17 Link na bio ou arrasta pra cima`\n    ];\n  } else if (estilo === 'educativo') {\n    return [\n      `\ud83c\udf93 Por que muita gente n\u00e3o vende online?`,\n      `\ud83d\ude30 Porque falta clareza, m\u00e9todo e dire\u00e7\u00e3o.`,\n      `\ud83d\udca1 O ${nome} resolve isso com:\\n\\n${promessa}`,\n      `\ud83d\udcd8 Baseado em:\\n${historia}`,\n      `\u2705 Aplique e colha os resultados!`,\n      `\ud83d\udcf2 Acesse agora e comece j\u00e1.`\n    ];\n  }\n  return [];\n}\n<\/script>\n<!-- JSZip e FileSaver -->\n<script src=\"https:\/\/cdnjs.cloudflare.com\/ajax\/libs\/jszip\/3.7.1\/jszip.min.js\"><\/script>\n<script src=\"https:\/\/cdnjs.cloudflare.com\/ajax\/libs\/FileSaver.js\/2.0.5\/FileSaver.min.js\"><\/script>\n\n<!-- Bot\u00e3o para baixar ZIP -->\n<div style=\"text-align:center; margin-top: 30px;\">\n  <button onclick=\"baixarTodasImagens()\" style=\"background: #3FF000; color: black; font-weight: bold; padding: 14px 24px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 18px; cursor: pointer;\">\n    \ud83d\udce6 Baixar todas as imagens em ZIP\n  <\/button>\n<\/div>\n\n<script>\nasync function baixarTodasImagens() {\n  const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.story-card');\n  if (cards.length === 0) {\n    alert(\"Gere os stories primeiro!\");\n    return;\n  }\n\n  const zip = new JSZip();\n  let count = 1;\n\n  for (const card of cards) {\n    const canvas = await html2canvas(card);\n    const dataUrl = canvas.toDataURL();\n    const imgData = dataUrl.split(',')[1];\n    zip.file(`story-${count}.png`, imgData, {base64: true});\n    count++;\n  }\n\n  zip.generateAsync({type: 'blob'}).then(content => {\n    saveAs(content, \"storytelling-PVO.zip\");\n  });\n}\n<\/script>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\ud83c\udfac Criador de Storytelling &#8211; PVO Nome do Produto: Promessa Principal: Storytelling \/ Hist\u00f3ria (curta): Estilo: EmocionalDiretoEducativo Cor de Fundo: Logo (opcional): \ud83d\ude80 Gerar Storytelling \ud83d\udce6 Baixar todas as imagens em ZIP<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"elementor_header_footer","meta":{"_uag_custom_page_level_css":"","footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-4090","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"uagb_featured_image_src":{"full":false,"thumbnail":false,"medium":false,"medium_large":false,"large":false,"1536x1536":false,"2048x2048":false},"uagb_author_info":{"display_name":"Kenin","author_link":"https:\/\/blog.primeiravendaonlinebr.com\/author\/kennedyfrancocarvalhogmail-com\/"},"uagb_comment_info":0,"uagb_excerpt":"\ud83c\udfac Criador de Storytelling &#8211; PVO Nome do Produto: Promessa Principal: Storytelling \/ Hist\u00f3ria (curta): Estilo: EmocionalDiretoEducativo Cor de Fundo: Logo (opcional): \ud83d\ude80 Gerar Storytelling \ud83d\udce6 Baixar todas as imagens em ZIP","_links":{"self":[{"href"